        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-primary/10 border border-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center text-primary text-2xl mx-auto mb-6 transition-all duration-500 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:border-primary group-hover:bg-primary/20 process-icon"><i class="fas fa-map"></i></div>
        <div class="text-3xl font-black text-primary/30 mb-2 leading-none process-num">02</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-black uppercase tracking-widest mb-3 text-white group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Strategy</h3>
        <p class="text-white/50 text-xs font-medium leading-relaxed max-w-xs mx-auto">A custom growth roadmap built around your goals, audience, and budget.</p>
